<!-- SC_OFF --><div class="md"><p>Reshimost is a &#39;simple engine&#39; written in C++ which is on development. it has smart vectors, fast math, has scenes &amp; entities, text rendering support, and loading sprites is pretty straightforward. it uses OpenGL 3.0 as a rendering back-end and the code is available for anyone to modify, redistribute, contribute or even sell.</p> <p><a href="https://imgur.com/a/6KkEZrc">Demo</a></p> <p><a href="https://github.com/0xhaku/reshimost/">Repository</a></p> </div><!-- SC_ON --> &#32; submitted by &#32; <a href="https://www.reddit.com/user/TypeRacerPlayer21478"> /u/TypeRacerPlayer21478 </a> <br/> <span><a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/linux/comments/w73z07/reshimost_another_free_and_open_source_game_engine/">[link]</a></span> &#32; <span><a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/linux/comments/w73z07/reshimost_another_free_and_open_source_game_engine/">[comments]</a></span>